{"h45e028a9g7727g4fd0g8be2g126d86b9d8f1": ["The doggies nearly got me this time. It was close.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "5365cec8-c283-2cd2-9540-1905ec5809cd"], "hca0e290fgb84fg4a28gba5dg14ad99eca23f": ["Not close enough. ", "8a064abd-3582-4a32-a9f8-748ad60f63ca", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "69f02bc5-0ce4-67e1-d164-b3a2759e5c39"], "had07b267g52f0g4209g8557g90873a01ae97": ["Lass, if you hate me that much, hire someone to kill me.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "03fd033d-aa22-dff9-b0c7-c9f8ed50d73e"], "hc2de439egda3bg4988g9752gd70f9a1d902b": ["My way's cheaper.", "8a064abd-3582-4a32-a9f8-748ad60f63ca", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "2561c96f-1f19-c3b6-7fcb-b20158a02845"], "h6d16f57eg308eg40cag93f1g97881d63be62": ["I'm told we're taking a stroll through the Underdark once we blow the charges.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "68d4eaf2-fe67-a5e6-d891-56f69482c10b"], "hc817ed37g68aeg4addg8cbbg731a61974095": ["Let me guess. You'd rather take the surface.", "8a064abd-3582-4a32-a9f8-748ad60f63ca", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "fcc53056-7585-8ef0-6a3a-e8f32c7a5c53"], "h6d64661egaed5g4a4bgace6g35caee8f7acc": ["The route with fewer hook horrors and other beasties? Perish the thought. ", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "b6c10e57-4156-af57-6b27-06173c87a69d"], "h4f15f230gb62fg42dagae7cg7cab5573d8b1": ["How did a coward like you survive all these years in the Network?", "8a064abd-3582-4a32-a9f8-748ad60f63ca", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "e4c61df9-c273-9772-e1a8-0048e5f3ab9d"], "hff7bb695g2eb5g472aga6c9g93a0d1512232": ["Avoiding the Underdark, for one. ", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "0a17b6d0-409f-8f5d-53fe-b687f0435e9e"], "h1043ed86g916dg4266gb8f9g39502caea806": ["I'm told we're taking a stroll through the Underdark once we blow the charges.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "d95ce77b-ab15-b695-1154-a988e933ec52"], "h525a578bg5b7eg4a3fg8528gddff39e9562f": ["I'm sick of hiding down in the dark. This ain't why I joined the Zahent!", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "162d2b5a-6693-b22e-b5ee-15123aa612df"], "h3f9da0a7gb77dg4755gbe96g2ca2d53454c3": ["It's pronounced 'Zent', lad. The H is silent. ", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "54608416-6ec3-c7d0-050e-b337cb0f7913"], "h29960490g7ca1g4fdbgbbf4gbda2b3dfb1d1": ["I don't care. I want out of this damn cave.", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "764aba96-5aee-5aef-0e4e-c0ab0c946d54"], "h2b14b53age8ffg470bg8214gf7ace2252516": ["Why, scared of gahosts?", "8a064abd-3582-4a32-a9f8-748ad60f63ca", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "d0707543-5b07-dc5f-e46c-c3e275dc311b"], "h948fda3bg87afg473cg91e9gdf3f4d6db455": ["You lot are always making fun of me.", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "c9115dc5-e270-630a-d2b3-c485db23e5f7"], "h47dcf565ga3b5g4b09gb2a9gaced7b3cbe10": ["Oh, lad. That just shows we care!", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "0a4f9443-b45f-232d-ed71-66cbde501202"], "h8d7304a4g8bb8g4bfegab7cg941b6084c829": ["I do it because it makes me hate him less.", "8a064abd-3582-4a32-a9f8-748ad60f63ca", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "7070e78f-dbe7-5458-b97c-334b2b87c214"], "h6df19ec9g2243g4af5g8d31ga3c76c2138c0": ["See? You're among friends.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents.html", "ada50bb2-dc84-43d8-33ef-186c9ad34b68"]}